data.description: This move-in ready 3 bed/2 bath home in the rural town of Climax is one you don't want to miss! On nearly half an acre lot this property offers a nice split floor plan, new LVP flooring and carpet throughout, new front and back deck, brand new outbuilding remains with the home and did I mention the spacious backyard? Perfect for all your favorite outdoor activities. Come check it out for yourself!
